|caption=An example of a {{music|time|3|4}} time signature. The time signature indicates that there are three [[quarter note]]s (crotchets) per [[measure (music)|measure]] (bar).
|alt=Printed music staff with treble-clef symbol, {{music|time|3|4}} time signature, and 3 quarter notes: A, F, and middle C.
